title: AutoQ3D CAD v2.2.3 [PD]
description:
AutoQ3D CAD is a full cad software tool to help you create 2D & 3D technical drawings and sketching designs as well.

AutoQ3D CAD is easy to use and fast for everybody as professionals, sketchers, architects, engineers, designers, students and more.

Also runs on android tablets, support surfaces and 3d formats like STL, OBJ, DXF and native 3DQ with textures, you could use the Desktop version(Windows/Linux) to print your drawings.

Drawing Tools
* Line
* Circle
* Rectangle
* Arc
* Polygon
* Text
* Triangles
* Box
* Sphere
* Extrude
* Revolve

Edit Tools
* Move
* Scale
* Stretch
* Rotate
* Array
* Mirror

Preset Views
* Top
* Front
* Rigth
* Bottom
* Back
* Left
* Isometric

View Tools
* Wireframe, smooth and hide lines mode.
* Show Normals
* Enable/disable lighting
* Rotate View
* Zoom
* Zoom All
* Pan
* Rotate

Modify Tools
* Trim
* Fillet
* Offset
* Extend
* Explode
* Slice
* Texture UV
* Normals operations

Snap Tools
* Endpoint
* Midpoint
* Nearest
* Intersection
* Center
* Grid

Misc Tools
* Grouping
* Distance
* Area
* STL, OBJ, DXF file support

What's New:

Selection improvements.
Bug fix in undo.
Region and extrude enhancement.
